.RS
.RE
.TP
.B \f[B]a\f[]
use local version
.RS
.RE
.TP
.B \f[B]d\f[]
use incoming version
.RS
.RE
.TP
.B \f[B]e\f[]
manually edit code
.RS
.RE
.TP
.B \f[B]j\f[]
scroll down
.RS
.RE
.TP
.B \f[B]k\f[]
scroll up
.RS
.RE
.TP
.B \f[B]v\f[]
[v]iew orientation
.RS
.RE
.TP
.B \f[B]n\f[]
[n]ext conflict
.RS
.RE
.TP
